    %h1 Week 7 "Crowdfunder" Assignment

    %p
      This week we'll be creating a crowd funding web app, like Kickstarter or Indiegogo.
      Project creators will be able to add projects that they want people to support. Users
      will be able to browse the projects, and make a pledge using a form.  Each funding level has a reward attached to it
      (e.g. Fund a project for $10 and get a free t-shirt).


    %p
